metadata.name: Midnight Glow
metadata.description:
The warm glow of a window on a cold winter night.

An edition to celebrate the one-year anniversary of my first collection in the NFT Space "Winter Wonderland" which was released in December 2021. This photo helps to bring everything full circle from last year and is one of my favorite winter shots Iâ€™ve captured. Shot in Steamboat Springs, Colorado, on a Mamiya RZ67.
